// AppointmentStatus: SCHEDULED, ARRIVED, WAITING, IN_CONSULTATION, COMPLETED, CANCELLED, NO_SHOW
// PaymentMethod: CASH, UPI, CARD, CHEQUE
// PaymentStatus: PENDING, PAID, PARTIAL, REFUNDED
